name: 2-oxoglutarate dehydrogenase
equation: [m] : akg + coa + nad --> co2 + nadh + succoa

name: citrate synthase
equation: [m] : accoa + h2o + oaa --> cit + coa + h

name: pyruvate dehydrogenase
equation: [m] : coa + nad + pyr --> accoa + co2 + nadh

name: Succinate--CoA ligase (GDP-forming)
equation: [m] : coa + gtp + succ <==> gdp + pi + succoa

name: Complex II reaction for respiratory chain

equation: adp[m] + (4) h[c] + pi[m] --> atp[m] + h2o[m] + (3) h[m]

name: ubiquinol-6 cytochrome c reductase, Complex III
L-lactate reversible transport via proton symport
pyruvate mitochondrial transport via proton symport
cytochrome c oxidase, mitochondrial Complex IV
